costumebot functionsmap

faces!
	default
		eyes
			lookleft,lookmidleft,lookmid.lookmidright,lookright
			blink,blinkmid,winkleft,winkright
		mouth
			smile, grin, grinopen
			phenomes
				oh, ah, ee, eff
	happy
		hypelaser (intro, loop)
		sparkle (3frames)
		nya, nyaha, nyaoh
	cranky
		angy
			angy01/02, talk, oh, grit, blink
		stressed
			stressed01, blink
		grump
			lookleft,lookmidleft,lookmid.lookmidright,lookright
			blink
		crying
			doeEyes, crywaterfall
	symbols
		NOface
		YESface
		testPattern, testPatternGlitch01,02,03
		sinewave
		bufferwheel
		glitchstatic (transition animations)
		lowBattery
	
	sinewave is MUSIC visualizer mode
		
body!
	default
		cool tones pink/purple/blue/aqua/SOME green and yellow sparkles
	happy
		hypelaser - orange & yellow pulse (indigo baseBG), with magentapurple wavestripes
		sparkle - purple with pink clouds and yellow glitter
		nya - pink and orange lavalamp
	cranky	
		angy - red fire!
		stressed - purple and red rain
		grump - green blocks
		crying - blue rain
	symbols
		NO and YES - default but with a wave or flash of related color
		testPattern - wipe cycle thru same colors in blocks
		sinewave - rainbow? very slow, reactive brightness
		bufferwheel - white waves that freeze, progressbar
		lowBattery - red heartbeat pulse
		
eventual option to hueshift default with remote

inputs!
	buttons
		sleep mode (behind neck, or power core)
		hall effect sensor "buttons" for gloves (thumb magnet)
	sensors
		piezos on leggings (thigh slap laughter)
		gyro for head movement (sound trigger)
	sounds
		voicebox with beeps overlay related to frequency/tone
		claps make drumkit sounds
	motions
		antenna up/down related to expression
			restAngle - default, sinewave
			up - happy
			down - cranky, NOface, lowBattery
		vibration sensors trigger 1 or 2 back motors (for the sounds)
			low or high sensitivity\
remote
	6keys
	2 rotary encoders
	mini TFT menu
	tiny TFT streamdeck buttons
	
